Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:10.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,丈母娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:24.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈帮我拿酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:27.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,自己拿吧\N小事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:44.60,ASS,,0,0,0,,两人一起住的时候\N都需要你多多照顾她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:46.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:52.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是这样也不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,那连我一起照顾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:01.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,不用客气\N请跟我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:04.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,我很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:09.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,是啊 所以常常加班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,由纪不要这样说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:15.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,这样吵架\N真让我妒忌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈我们没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈的饺子好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:39.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,你的就没这么好吃\N为什么这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:44.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,你的饺子都没熟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,不要这样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:54.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,女儿夫妻搬到家里来住\N已经过了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:02:01.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,原因是他们工作的超商
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:07.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,就开在我家的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:14.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,从之前的家通勤很累
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:24.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,三年前老公就过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:27.98,ASS,,0,0,0,,我就一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,过着平淡生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:55.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,听见由纪被宠爱的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,我忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:03.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,寂寞的感受开始强烈起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,小穴好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,小穴好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:51.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,看到由纪都已经长大了\N我身为妈妈的责任也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:15:02.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,之后我就应该过着身为女人的生活\N也该放下老公了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:08.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,藏在我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:12.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,的女人心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.81,ASS,,0,0,0,,看呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:24.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,由纪也长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,突然说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:38.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,不用跟我们客气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.81,ASS,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,爸爸都过世三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,如果遇到喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,没有那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,去找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈还很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,有意愿的话\N年轻男生也会来追喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:10.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈参加的网球社\N应该有很多人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,没有那个人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,这样喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:44.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈之后也是一个人过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:47.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,也不是随便挑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:57.81,ASS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,像你一样的人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:06.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈好像很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,所以答应让我们住进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.52,ASS,,0,0,0,,因为是自己女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,不是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.32,ASS,,0,0,0,,我以为没人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,我洗太久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,只是一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,没被看到裸体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:04.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,被看到的那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:11.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,也意识到对方是女儿老公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:18.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,让我想起以前的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:23.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,也是因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,几天后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:30.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,我网球社的教练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,鲛岛教练到我家来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:41.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,为了忘掉宪明的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,不只是网球\N料理也很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:19.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,就算这样说也不会有什么好处喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.81,ASS,,0,0,0,,我去泡茶喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:26.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,鲛岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:45.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,在没人的时候叫我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:49.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.14,0:27:17.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.34,0:27:40.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,也帮我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.06,0:28:05.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,爽吗\N好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.70,0:28:21.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.26,0:29:20.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.82,0:29:24.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.70,0:29:25.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,多舔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.46,0:29:35.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,到上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.38,0:30:07.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.10,0:30:50.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.14,0:31:27.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.38,0:31:57.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.86,0:32:01.32,ASS,,0,0,0,,还要吗\N再来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.82,0:32:04.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.54,0:32:15.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.74,0:32:35.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,我也想舔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.66,0:32:48.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,我也想舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.86,0:32:51.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.54,0:32:53.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.94,0:33:11.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.74,0:33:22.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.30,0:33:49.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.29,0:34:09.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,这样好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.25,0:34:29.32,ASS,,0,0,0,,想看吗\N想
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.66,0:34:30.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.86,0:34:31.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,帮我脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.46,0:34:49.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.86,0:35:26.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.62,0:35:31.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,超爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.06,0:36:33.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.06,0:36:37.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,超爽的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.34,0:36:50.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.54,0:36:51.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.82,0:37:03.17,ASS,,0,0,0,,可以躺着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.94,0:37:45.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.06,0:37:53.17,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.10,0:38:26.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,我受不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.90,0:38:30.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.70,0:38:34.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.54,0:38:59.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,插入了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.78,0:39:03.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,屁股翘高
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.94,0:39:23.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,来了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.50,0:39:28.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.90,0:39:50.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.06,0:40:14.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.06,0:42:43.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.42,0:42:48.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,趴着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.54,0:43:51.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.50,0:43:56.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,插深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.38,0:45:13.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.34,0:45:28.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.78,0:45:43.81,ASS,,0,0,0,,翘高喔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.66,0:46:30.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.90,0:46:48.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.62,0:47:05.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.58,0:47:28.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.62,0:47:35.81,ASS,,0,0,0,,插入了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.70,0:48:31.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.50,0:48:36.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,好淫荡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.06,0:48:52.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,再来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.18,0:49:42.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.10,0:50:30.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.02,0:50:37.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,多舔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.74,0:52:25.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.70,0:52:47.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.54,0:53:57.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.10,0:54:00.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,我也要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.74,0:54:12.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.70,0:54:17.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,要射了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.90,0:55:00.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,好久没体会到的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.86,0:55:03.81,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.62,0:55:06.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是好像有点无奈
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.46,0:55:17.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,内心处好像有宪明的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.38,0:55:51.81,ASS,,0,0,0,,竟然很在意女儿的老公
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.22,0:55:58.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,为了掩盖这样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.86,0:56:01.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,和不喜欢的男人上床
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.30,0:56:07.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,老实说我的内心很混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.26,0:56:27.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,宪明要不要喝点茶
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.58,0:56:30.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.10,0:56:32.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.70,0:56:33.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,由纪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.58,0:56:39.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,好像跟高中同学去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.66,0:56:41.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,很早就出门了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.58,0:56:46.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,你很难得的休假
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.62,0:56:47.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.94,0:56:51.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈不需要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.34,0:57:02.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.02,0:57:04.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.70,0:57:05.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.26,0:57:10.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.34,0:57:14.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,今天要一起吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.10,0:57:17.40,ASS,,0,0,0,,好像附近有新开一间店
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.14,0:57:20.60,ASS,,0,0,0,,网球社的人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.82,0:57:22.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,网球
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.70,0:57:26.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,我去泡茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.98,0:57:46.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,宪明
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.10,0:57:50.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.02,0:57:54.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是我一看见那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.62,0:58:03.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,我昨天看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.90,0:58:09.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈和男人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.90,0:58:19.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,我都看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.18,0:58:28.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,不可以这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.06,0:58:32.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.74,0:58:35.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,我好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.26,0:58:38.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢着妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.94,0:58:42.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,冷静一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.62,0:58:44.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,你是由纪的老公喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.34,0:58:54.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,所以我一直忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.30,0:58:57.17,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.98,0:59:04.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.30,0:59:13.17,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.46,0:59:21.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.86,0:59:26.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,宪明
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.70,0:59:29.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,和我的想法一样
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.90,0:59:32.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.66,0:59:38.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.78,0:59:40.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,不可以这样想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.58,0:59:44.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,所以我才和那个人做了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.58,0:59:50.60,ASS,,0,0,0,,但是就算做爱了\N还是想着宪明
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.46,0:59:54.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.90,0:59:57.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,只有现在
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.66,1:00:00.04,ASS,,0,0,0,,在女儿回来之前
